1. *Povremeno* volim da idem u bioskop. (I occasionally like to go to the cinema.)
2. Volim *povremeno* da čitam knjige. (I like to read books from time to time.)
3. *Povremeno* se osećam umorno i iscrpljeno. (Occasionally, I feel tired and exhausted.)
4. Ona *povremeno* putuje u inostranstvo. (She occasionally travels abroad.)
5. *Povremeno* ću provesti vikend na planini. (I will occasionally spend a weekend in the mountains.)
6. Planinarim *povremeno* tokom leta. (I go hiking occasionally during the summer.)
7. *Povremeno* se setim svojih starih prijatelja. (I occasionally remember my old friends.)
8. *Povremeno* izlazim s prijateljima u grad. (I occasionally go out with friends in the city.)
9. Kupujem *povremeno* nove knjige za svoju biblioteku. (I occasionally buy new books for my library.)
10. *Povremeno* ću se opustiti uz dobru muziku. (I will occasionally relax with good music.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "povremeno" means "occasionally" or "from time to time". The star (*) has been placed before the word "povremeno" in each sentence to highlight it.